data.description: Welcome to an extraordinary residence in the highly sought-after Avalon Subdivision, where luxury meets functionality. This exquisite home, boasts a laundry list of upgrades & customized finishes sure to impress. Step inside to find a completely turnkey home w/freshly painted interior, upgraded LVP flooring, new bathroom & kitchen fixtures & lighting. Situated on an oversized prime lot, offering unparalleled serenity & tranquility. Spacious interior boasts 5 bdrs/3 full bthr & oversized bonus.  Marvel at the gorgeous fireplace w/gorgeous custom mantle. Open concept kitchen has recently purchased SS appliances. Witness the beauty of the four seasons in the custom screened in porch. Professionally designed paver patio w/oversized fireplace & lighting makes this home an exceptional find. Minutes from everything Downtown Mooresville has to offer! Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to own a turnkey property that is more than a home; it's a lifestyle upgrade waiting for your family.
